data.description: This charming residence seamlessly blends elegance with comfort offering a perfect haven for a discerning buyer.  Boasting 3 bedrooms plus a den, this home provides versatile living spaces that cater to both relaxation and productivity.  The two bathrooms along with a pool bath feature modern amenities, ensuring both convenience and style.  With marble flooring throughout most of the 2,216 sq ft home, the outdoor atmosphere is further highlighted by the tiki bar, outdoor fridge and sink.  Cozy up in front of the wood-burning fireplace, or take a dip in the pool if you’re feeling hot.  You can even rinse off under the outdoor shower.  Crown molding embellishes the interior, and each room features sliders that lead out to the pool and tiki bar.  Situated on one of the largest lots in the neighborhood, this property provides ample space for outdoor activities and potential expansion.  The attached service garage faces the backyard and is the only one available in the community.  It’s perfect for storing lawn equipment, sporting goods, or even woodworking!  Another unique feature of this home is its picturesque backdrop – an expansive horse farm directly behind the property, offering a tranquil and idyllic setting.  Experience the allure of country living while still enjoying the comforts of a well-appointed home.  This property presents a rare opportunity to embrace the best of both worlds, combining spacious luxury with the charm of rural landscapes.  Don’t miss the chance to make this extraordinary residence your new home!  Roof replaced with 25 year shingles in 2014, A/C replaced in May 2019, Water Heater replaced in July 2021 and Washer replaced in Sept. 2022.
